	 Variables can be shortened to 3 characters. Example: <br> =%<nop>GMTIME{"$day $month, $year - $hour:$min:$sec"}%= is <br> <b>%GMTIME{"$day $month, $year - $hour:$min:$sec"}%</b> </td>
